=== Subsidiary Shrines ===
Of the 11 subsidiary shrines, 8 are enshrined together in the subordinate shrine building of Nishinomiya Shrine. Orihime Shrine was destroyed by fire, and Itsukushima Shrine collapsed and has not been rebuilt.
* Nishinomiya Shrine
* Sumiyoshi Shrine
* Raiden Shrine / Atago Shrine
