=== Access ===
* 15 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Iwafune Station|Q11475586|qid=Q11475586|1=Iwafune Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Ryōmō Line|Q253391|qid=Q253391|lt=JR Ryōmō Line|1=Ryōmō Line}}
* About 25 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Sano-Fujioka Interchange|Q10885981|qid=Q10885981|lt=Sano-Fujioka I.C.|1=Sano-Fujioka interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Tōhoku Expressway|Q428428|qid=Q428428|1=Tōhoku Expressway}}
* 40 minutes from Tochigi Station on the JR Ryōmō Line / {{ill|lt=Tōbu Nikkō Line|Q845954|qid=Q845954|1=Tōbu Nikkō Line}} via the Tochigi City Fureai Bus Minagawa Hinokuchi Line bound for “Yurarakukan”
** Get off at “Murahi Shrine Entrance” bus stop, 5-minute walk (few services)
** Get off at “Eda Clinic-mae” bus stop, 20-minute walk

